Internationally renowned choreographer and dancer, Gregory Maqoma, has made a reputable name for himself as a story teller who speaks volumes through dance. As the head of noted Vuyani Dance Theatre, Maqoma has used his experience to usher in a new fleet of talents. We speak to the legendary dancer about making a business of his talent and how he continuous to remain innovative. For more episodes,click here. Do you have an inspiring story to tell? Are you an entrepreneur making big moves? Do you know of a small business that needs more support? Share your stories with us via e-mail sebenza@sowetanlive.co.za or reach out to us on social media @SebenzaLIVE on Twitter or Instagram. Subscribe: iono.fm | Spotify | Pocket Casts | Player.fm​